{"tid":2507863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登提名台裔盧沛寧 任聯合國改革與管理事務代表","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T12:35:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f175daff780a8db413dd38966fa3c48a84981ca","tid":2507863,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"拜登提名台裔盧沛寧 任聯合國改革與管理事務代表<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%B0%E8%A3%94%E7%9B%A7%E6%B2%9B%E5%AF%A7-%E4%BB%BB%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-023413180.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%259B%25A7%25E6%25B2%259B%25E5%25AF%25A7-%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8-023413180.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0priIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=12713958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%B0%E8%A3%94%E7%9B%A7%E6%B2%9B%E5%AF%A7-%E4%BB%BB%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-023413180.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登27號提出兩項人事任命案，都是台灣出生的移民第二代，除了被提名出任美國國防部「研發暨工程部」副部長的女科學家徐若冰，另一位是出任駐聯合國改革與管理事務代表，等同大使身份的盧沛寧。<br />\n<br />\n盧沛寧的父母都在中國大陸出生，1949年在台灣短暫生活一段時間後，1950年代赴美留學，並移民當地。1966年6月12號，盧沛寧在美國新澤西州出生。<br />\n<br />\n盧沛寧是美國前總統歐巴馬在哈佛法學院的同學，歐巴馬主政期間，她擔任白宮的內閣秘書長，曾被認為是歐巴馬政府中最具影響力的人。"},{"pid":"b2e728f1ab7354b31a1aa6dd16fceee067c515da","tid":2507863,"uid":155784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"UN有台灣代表了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=